---
title: Lemony Pesto Penne and Summer Veggies with Basil and Goat Cheese
description: Sunshine in a bowl! This bright pasta dinner brings together all the complementary flavours of summer: zucchini, tomatoes, goat cheese, a hint of lemon and a touch of basil!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pennes-au-pesto-citronne-et-aux-legumes-estivaux-082d0246.jpg
